  volumenAudio: 0.8
  textoFragmento: "Child.\r\nThere it is... the main door.\r\nFinally... I can get
    out.\r\nCome on, open up!\r\nWhat...?\r\nNo... that can\u2019t be...\r\nA hand?
    Please let it be a toy... old... wrinkled... it\u2019s holding a chain...\r\nIt\u2019s
    moving!\r\nLet go... let go!\r\nNothing... I can\u2019t... it\u2019s gripping
    too tight\u2026\r\n\r\nwitch\r\nSomeone\u2019s turned on the light! There are
    intruders in my house!\r"
